@startuml
[*] --> CreateUser : user chooses to create account
CreateUser : entry / nil
CreateUser : do / Create account
CreateUser : exit / Login

Login : entry / nil
Login : do / Login
Login : exit / Application

Login --> Application : user logs in

Application : entry / Login
Application : do / Apply for visa
Application : exit / Payment

Application --> Payment : user applies for visa

Payment : entry / Application
Payment : do / Make payment
Payment : exit / Accepted

Payment --> Accepted : payment made

Accepted : entry / Payment
Accepted : do / Accept application
Accepted : exit / Status

Accepted --> Status : application accepted

Status : entry / Accepted
Status : do / View status
Status --> CheckStatus : user views status

CheckStatus : entry / Status
CheckStatus : do / Check status
CheckStatus --> Cancel : [valid] user checks status and cancels application
CheckStatus --> GiveFeedback : [valid] user checks status and gives feedback

Cancel : entry / CheckStatus
Cancel : do / Cancel application
Cancel --> Logout : user cancels application

ModifyDetails : entry / Login
ModifyDetails : do / Modify details
ModifyDetails --> Logout : [valid] user modifies details

ViewDetails : entry / Login
ViewDetails : do / View details
ViewDetails --> Logout : [valid] user views details

ViewPurpose : entry / Login
ViewPurpose : do / View purpose
ViewPurpose --> UpdateStatus : [valid] user views purpose and updates status

UpdateStatus : entry / ViewPurpose
UpdateStatus : do / Update status
UpdateStatus --> Logout : [valid] user updates status

GiveFeedback : entry / CheckStatus
GiveFeedback : do / Give feedback
GiveFeedback --> Logout : [valid] user gives feedback

Logout : entry / nil
Logout : do / Logout
Logout --> [*] : user logs out

CreateUser --> Login : user creates account

Login --> Application : user logs in

Application --> Payment : user applies for visa

Payment --> Accepted : payment made

Accepted --> Status : application accepted

Status --> CheckStatus : user views status

Choice1 --> CreateUser : user chooses to create account
Choice2 --> Login : user chooses to log in
Choice3 --> Application : user chooses to apply for visa
Choice4 --> ModifyDetails : user chooses to modify details
Choice5 --> ViewDetails : user chooses to view details
Choice6 --> ViewPurpose : user chooses to view purpose
Choice7 --> GiveFeedback : user chooses to give feedback
Choice8 --> Cancel : user chooses to cancel application
Choice9 --> UpdateStatus : user chooses to update status

ModifyDetails --> Logout : [valid] user modifies details

ViewDetails --> Logout : [valid] user views details

ViewPurpose --> UpdateStatus : [valid] user views purpose and updates status

UpdateStatus --> Logout : [valid] user updates status

GiveFeedback --> Logout : [valid] user gives feedback

CheckStatus --> Cancel : [invalid] user checks status and cancels application
CheckStatus --> GiveFeedback : [invalid] user checks status and gives feedback

Choice10 --> Status : user chooses to view status
Choice11 --> Logout : user chooses to log out

@enduml
